These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: hiking, rock-climbing
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: blues, salsa
1. the fan of blues is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is not to the right of the fan of salsa##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |
| Hobby        | hiking   | rock-climbing   |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | blues |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, nigerian
2 different pets are kept: fish, turtle
1. the owner of the fish is not to the left of the nigerian##8
2. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the right of the nigerian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| Nationality   | nigerian | dutch   |
| Pet      | turtle | fish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-3::.
House: cottage, craftsman
City: miami, san-francisco
1. the cottage house is not to the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##8
2. the craftsman house is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| House          | craftsman | cottage |
| City   | miami   | san-francisco     |

